# рҹ“Ў Dokumentasi API вҖ” SCM MBG Backend
ini untuk url nya nanti di env
**https://scm-modullogistik-production.up.railway.app
`  
**Format Response:** JSON  


> [!IMPORTANT]
> Semua response mengikuti format standar:
> ```json
> { "success": true, "data": {...}, "count": 10, "message": "..." }
> ```

---

## 1. рҹҸ« Schools (Master Data Sekolah)
**Base:** `/api/schools`

| Method | Endpoint | Kegunaan |
|--------|----------|----------|
| `GET` | `/api/schools` | Ambil semua data sekolah (nama, alamat, koordinat, jumlah porsi) |
| `GET` | `/api/schools/:id` | Ambil detail satu sekolah |
| `POST` | `/api/schools` | Tambah sekolah baru |
| `PUT` | `/api/schools/:id` | Update data sekolah |
| `DELETE` | `/api/schools/:id` | Hapus sekolah |
| `GET` | `/api/schools/stats/portions` | Statistik total porsi per sekolah (untuk dashboard) |
| `GET` | `/api/schools/geocode?q=...` | Geocoding alamat вҶ’ koordinat GPS |
| `POST` | `/api/schools/login` | **Login akun sekolah** вҖ” untuk mobile app modul feedback |

**Data yang dikembalikan tiap sekolah:**
```json
{
  "_id": "...",
  "name": "SDN Lengkong 01",
  "address": "Jl. Lengkong Besar No.12...",
  "location": { "type": "Point", "coordinates": [107.61, -6.92] },
  "totalStudents": 320,
  "portionsNeeded": 320,
  "contactPerson": "Ibu Sari Mulyani",
  "phone": "08123...",
  "district": "Lengkong",
  "username": "sdn_lengkong01"
}
```

> [!NOTE]
> Field `password` **tidak pernah dikembalikan** di response manapun (disimpan sebagai hash bcrypt di server).

**`POST /api/schools/login` вҖ” untuk mobile app:**

Body:
```json
{ "username": "sdn_lengkong01", "password": "mbg2024" }
```

Response sukses:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "_id": "...",
    "name": "SDN Lengkong 01",
    "username": "sdn_lengkong01",
    "totalStudents": 320,
    "portionsNeeded": 320,
    "district": "Lengkong"
  }
}
```

Response gagal (username/password salah):
```json
{ "success": false, "message": "Username atau password salah" }
```

**Alur lengkap mobile app setelah login:**
```
Step 1 вҖ” Login:
  POST /api/schools/login
  вҶ’ simpan _id dari response sebagai schoolId

Step 2 вҖ” Ambil data siswa sekolah ini:
  GET /api/students/school/{schoolId}
  вҶ’ hanya mengembalikan siswa milik sekolah yang login,
    tidak akan bocor data siswa sekolah lain
```

**Dibutuhkan oleh modul:** Load Planning, Route Optimization, Live Monitoring, Analytics, **Mobile App Feedback (login sekolah)**

---

## 2. рҹ‘ЁвҖҚрҹҺ“ Students (Data Siswa)
**Base:** `/api/students`

| Method | Endpoint | Kegunaan |
|--------|----------|----------|
| `GET` | `/api/students` | Ambil semua siswa (bisa filter dengan `?schoolId=...`) |
| `GET` | `/api/students/school/:schoolId` | Ambil semua siswa dari satu sekolah |
| `POST` | `/api/students` | Tambah siswa baru |
| `PUT` | `/api/students/:id` | Update data siswa |
| `DELETE` | `/api/students/:id` | Hapus siswa |

**Data yang dikembalikan:**
```json
{
  "_id": "...",
  "name": "Budi Santoso",
  "studentId": "STD-001",
  "className": "6A",
  "school": { "_id": "...", "name": "SDN Menteng 01" },
  "isActive": true
}
```

**Dibutuhkan oleh modul:** Master Data (referensi jumlah porsi per sekolah)

---

## 3. рҹҡӣ Vehicles (Armada Kendaraan)
**Base:** `/api/vehicles`

| Method | Endpoint | Kegunaan |
|--------|----------|----------|
| `GET` | `/api/vehicles` | Ambil semua kendaraan beserta driver yang assigned |
| `GET` | `/api/vehicles/:id` | Detail satu kendaraan |
| `POST` | `/api/vehicles` | Tambah kendaraan baru |
| `PUT` | `/api/vehicles/:id` | Update data kendaraan |
| `DELETE` | `/api/vehicles/:id` | Hapus kendaraan |
| `POST` | `/api/vehicles/:id/assign-driver` | Assign driver ke kendaraan |
| `DELETE` | `/api/vehicles/:id/remove-driver/:driverId` | Lepas driver dari kendaraan |

**Data yang dikembalikan:**
```json
{
  "_id": "...",
  "plateNumber": "B 1234 MBG",
  "type": "Box",
  "capacity": 350,
  "status": "available",
  "brand": "Mitsubishi",
  "fuelType": "Solar",
  "assignedDrivers": [{ "_id": "...", "name": "...", "status": "available" }],
  "currentLocation": { "coordinates": [106.84, -6.19] }
}
```

**Status kendaraan:** `available` | `in_use` | `maintenance`

**Dibutuhkan oleh modul:** Load Planning (kapasitas), Route Optimization, Live Monitoring, Analytics

