## 5. рҹ“Ұ Load Plans (Perencanaan Muatan + Delivery Plan)
**Base:** `/api/load-plans`

| Method | Endpoint | Kegunaan |
|--------|----------|----------|
| `GET` | `/api/load-plans/ready-portions` | Ambil data porsi siap dari modul produksi (mock Noval) |
| `GET` | `/api/load-plans/production-status` | Status produksi dapur saat ini |
| `POST` | `/api/load-plans/calculate` | **Jalankan algoritma First-Fit Decreasing** вҶ’ hitung distribusi porsi per kendaraan |
| `GET` | `/api/load-plans` | Ambil semua delivery plan yang sudah disimpan |
| `POST` | `/api/load-plans` | Simpan delivery plan baru ke database |
| `PATCH` | `/api/load-plans/:id/status` | Update status plan (`planned`вҶ’`loading`вҶ’`in_transit`вҶ’`completed`) |

**Body `POST /calculate`:**
```json
{ "date": "2026-06-11", "schoolIds": ["id1", "id2"] }
```

**Body `POST /` (simpan delivery plan):**
```json
{
  "date": "2026-06-11",
  "vehicle": "vehicleId",
  "driver": "driverId",
  "schools": [{ "school": "schoolId", "portions": 320 }],
  "totalPortions": 320,
  "status": "planned"
}
```

**Response `GET /ready-portions`:**
```json
{
  "kitchen": "Dapur Pusat MBG Jakarta",
  "totalPortionsReady": 4200,
  "totalPortionsOrdered": 4500,
  "schools": [{ "schoolName": "...", "portionsReady": 320, "status": "ready", "menuItems": [...] }]
}
```

**Status delivery plan:** `planned` | `loading` | `in_transit` | `completed` | `cancelled`

**Dibutuhkan oleh modul:** Route Optimization, Live Monitoring, Proof of Delivery, Analytics

---

## 6. рҹ—әпёҸ Routes (Optimasi Rute)
**Base:** `/api/routes`

| Method | Endpoint | Kegunaan |
|--------|----------|----------|
| `POST` | `/api/routes/optimize` | Hitung rute optimal untuk satu kendaraan (Haversine/OSRM) |
| `GET` | `/api/routes` | Ambil semua rute yang tersimpan |
| `GET` | `/api/routes/:planId` | Ambil rute berdasarkan delivery plan ID |

**Body `POST /optimize`:**
```json
{
  "originCoords": [106.8456, -6.2088],
  "schoolIds": ["id1", "id2", "id3"],
  "deliveryPlanId": "planId",
  "useOSRM": true
}
```

**Dibutuhkan oleh modul:** Live Monitoring (tampilkan jalur di peta)

---

## 7. рҹ“Қ Tracking (Live Monitoring GPS)
**Base:** `/api/tracking`

| Method | Endpoint | Kegunaan |
|--------|----------|----------|
| `POST` | `/api/tracking/update` | Update posisi GPS kendaraan secara realtime |
| `GET` | `/api/tracking/active/all` | Ambil posisi semua kendaraan yang sedang aktif |
| `GET` | `/api/tracking/:planId` | Tracking terkini untuk satu delivery plan |
| `GET` | `/api/tracking/:planId/history` | Riwayat pergerakan kendaraan |

**Body `POST /update`:**
```json
{
  "deliveryPlanId": "...",
  "coordinates": [106.84, -6.19],
  "speed": 45,
  "heading": 180,
  "status": "in_transit",
  "battery": 85
}
```

> [!NOTE]
> Selain REST API, tracking juga bisa dilakukan via **Socket.io** dengan event `location_update`.
> Socket URL: `https://scm-modullogistik-production.up.railway.app` вҖ” join room `monitoring`.

---

## 8. вң… Deliveries / Proof of Delivery (Bukti Pengiriman)
**Base:** `/api/deliveries`

| Method | Endpoint | Kegunaan |
|--------|----------|----------|
| `GET` | `/api/deliveries` | Ambil semua catatan pengiriman (bisa filter `?status=delivered`) |
| `POST` | `/api/deliveries` | Buat delivery records dari sebuah delivery plan |
| `GET` | `/api/deliveries/plan/:planId` | Ambil semua pengiriman dari satu delivery plan |
| `POST` | `/api/deliveries/:id/confirm` | Konfirmasi pengiriman + upload foto bukti (`multipart/form-data`) |
| `PATCH` | `/api/deliveries/:id/status` | Update status pengiriman |

**Status pengiriman:** `pending` | `delivered` | `rejected`

**Body `POST /:id/confirm` (form-data):**
- `photo` вҖ” file foto bukti pengiriman
- `receivedBy` вҖ” nama penerima
- `signature` вҖ” tanda tangan (base64)
- `notes` вҖ” catatan tambahan
- `temperature` вҖ” suhu makanan (opsional)

---

## 9. рҹ“Ҡ Analytics (Laporan & Performa)
**Base:** `/api/analytics`

| Method | Endpoint | Kegunaan |
|--------|----------|----------|
| `GET` | `/api/analytics/dashboard` | Statistik ringkasan untuk dashboard utama |
| `GET` | `/api/analytics/performance?month=6&year=2026` | Laporan performa bulanan (on-time rate, completion rate) |
| `GET` | `/api/analytics/fuel-efficiency` | Efisiensi bahan bakar per kendaraan |
| `GET` | `/api/analytics/on-time-rate` | Tingkat ketepatan waktu pengiriman |

**Response `GET /dashboard`:**
```json
{
  "totalSchools": 25,
  "totalVehicles": 10,
  "availableVehicles": 7,
  "totalDrivers": 12,
  "activeDrivers": 8,
  "todayDeliveryPlans": 5,
  "totalPortionsNeeded": 4500,
  "systemStatus": "active"
}
```

