## 10. вқӨпёҸ Health Check
| Method | Endpoint | Kegunaan |
|--------|----------|----------|
| `GET` | `/api/health` | Cek apakah server aktif |

**Response:**
```json
{ "status": "ok", "timestamp": "2026-06-11T...", "uptime": 1234 }
```

---

## рҹ”Ң Socket.io вҖ” Realtime Events

**URL:** `http://localhost:5001`

| Event | Arah | Data | Kegunaan |
|-------|------|------|----------|
| `join_monitoring` | Client вҶ’ Server | вҖ” | Masuk ke room monitoring |
| `location_update` | Client вҶ’ Server | `{ deliveryPlanId, coordinates, speed, heading, status, battery }` | Driver kirim GPS |
| `vehicle_location_updated` | Server вҶ’ Client | `{ planId, location, speed, ... }` | Broadcast posisi ke semua monitor |
| `delivery_status_changed` | Server вҶ’ Client | `{ planId, status }` | Notifikasi perubahan status pengiriman |

---

## рҹ—ӮпёҸ Ringkasan Ketergantungan Antar Modul

```
Modul Produksi  в”Җв”ҖвҶ’ /api/load-plans/ready-portions
                                    вҶ“
                         /api/load-plans/calculate (FFD)
                                    вҶ“
                         /api/load-plans (simpan delivery plan)
                                    вҶ“
           в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ
           вҶ“                                     вҶ“
  /api/routes/optimize               /api/deliveries (buat POD records)
           вҶ“                                     вҶ“
  /api/tracking (GPS realtime)        /api/deliveries/:id/confirm
           вҶ“                                     вҶ“
           в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҖвҶ’ /api/analytics вҶҗв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ
```

| Data yang Dibutuhkan Modul Lain | Endpoint yang Dipanggil |
|---------------------------------|------------------------|
| Daftar sekolah + koordinat + porsi | `GET /api/schools` |
| Kendaraan tersedia + kapasitas | `GET /api/vehicles` |
| Driver tersedia | `GET /api/drivers` |
| Delivery plan aktif hari ini | `GET /api/load-plans` |
| Status pengiriman realtime | `GET /api/tracking/active/all` atau Socket.io |
| Porsi siap dari dapur | `GET /api/load-plans/ready-portions` |
| **Login sekolah (mobile app feedback)** | **`POST /api/schools/login`** |
